{"tid":2474862,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得支持劇透就要bam嗰啲人就好似小學生俾人改花名就逼個老師要將對方退學","createTime":"2021-04-04T09:13:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T07:30:34.000Z","uid":57911,"like":36,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0416f1f83417c236065cb6058027e3f53ba7ac15","tid":2474862,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T09:13:18.000Z","msg":"利申先我係支持admin處理劇透問題<br />\n但一定唔係睇人數處理<br />\n更加唔係用依樣做理由走去滅聲<br />\n追po成日見到人覺得bam咗天下太平<br />\n覺得俾人bam咗係抵撚死自己攞嚟<br />\n到講返咩理由要bam原來係劇透你話笑唔笑死人<br />\n成件事好似小學生改花名告俾老師知咁on9<br />\nadmin除咗bam人根本可以喺各種手段做嘢防止劇透<br />\n時事台搬po就咁撚快<br />\n依家有人玩嘢劇透就直接玩滅聲？<br />\n依啲咩比例嘅懲罰嚟<br />\n上面有一堆方法處理都好過滅聲<br />\n轉色、改標題、搬po、開漫畫台、鎖po、限推<br />\n全部都係一啲實在可行嘅方式阻止劇透<br />\n從來未聽過小學生因為改花名要退學咁霸道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e33aac42018fb83425dfb23fbbaaa7169d8ee8b8","tid":2474862,"uid":25771,"like":10,"dislike":9,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T09:17:56.000Z","msg":"你動機不良，管理員做嘢合情合理"},{"pid":"95ce720743a863a9c1d3cee5d289b9dfb23ac45d","tid":2474862,"uid":370062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T09:21:59.000Z","msg":"連狗，我們到了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2474706\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2474706</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"55c858b8e75d406917ed8218d10ef3e6569ae6b1","tid":2474862,"uid":19178,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T09:27:55.000Z","msg":"樓主人如其名<br />\n高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626aa2a3469b9feea6fe8aba90e23639383ee389","tid":2474862,"uid":57911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e33aac42018fb83425dfb23fbbaaa7169d8ee8b8","tid":2474862,"uid":25771,"like":10,"dislike":9,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T09:17:56.000Z","msg":"你動機不良，管理員做嘢合情合理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T09:29:39.000Z","msg":"我撐admin做嘢唔代表要撐佢bam人<br />\n次次admin唔滿意就要驅逐人<br />\n咁本身嗰啲平時正常一齊討論嘅人<br />\n因為一兩單嘢唔滿意就踩線作反<br />\n係唔係要以後都少個人討論"},{"pid":"34e0119516d5dc6cf125b03b8ba3ded78935dc4d","tid":2474862,"uid":105678,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"e33aac42018fb83425dfb23fbbaaa7169d8ee8b8","tid":2474862,"uid":25771,"like":10,"dislike":9,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T09:17:56.000Z","msg":"你動機不良，管理員做嘢合情合理"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T09:33:07.000Z","msg":"你動機不良，所以宇宙國安法捉鳩你合情合理"},{"pid":"7586077a93580e2755d1b367579a6f75ce631428","tid":2474862,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T10:36:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ed211766257d6578967b766e1874ae9b8a6a5cd","tid":2474862,"uid":305269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"34e0119516d5dc6cf125b03b8ba3ded78935dc4d","tid":2474862,"uid":105678,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"e33aac42018fb83425dfb23fbbaaa7169d8ee8b8","tid":2474862,"uid":25771,"like":10,"dislike":9,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T09:17:56.000Z","msg":"你動機不良，管理員做嘢合情合理"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T09:33:07.000Z","msg":"你動機不良，所以宇宙國安法捉鳩你合情合理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T10:38:12.000Z","msg":"電腦大爆炸<br />\n解放軍獲發宇宙通行證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8855675c2126c05357cf3d74f634fdade517e2d5","tid":2474862,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T11:43:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c331e58c7848acf04e86ee5678332215236e09b1","tid":2474862,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T13:10:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a91d94f4d716602256bb0acccee271ae2fd9504","tid":2474862,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T13:13:54.000Z","msg":"龍三難得有一次真係高質"},{"pid":"8d01d971145f2d58dc9c717b43639a927b298f6c","tid":2474862,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T15:36:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43c7c4b79a18e1ff28f5e129f4692f2a7f5aa69a","tid":2474862,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T05:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d68efc36456a58a880a077eb91d4ecf16995362","tid":2474862,"uid":38805,"like":8,"dislike":7,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T05:51:59.000Z","msg":"垃圾post 咪推啦, 處劇透撚仲講到為大義而戰收皮啦, 剩係見到你地日日洗板就覺得好L 煩."},{"pid":"d676a98be385401f4aaff3e0d867ebe0497a4167","tid":2474862,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6d68efc36456a58a880a077eb91d4ecf16995362","tid":2474862,"uid":38805,"like":8,"dislike":7,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T05:51:59.000Z","msg":"垃圾post 咪推啦, 處劇透撚仲講到為大義而戰收皮啦, 剩係見到你地日日洗板就覺得好L 煩."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T06:22:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d040e554672b0f4f661583b7a06c3d1f71f70a6d","tid":2474862,"uid":57911,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6d68efc36456a58a880a077eb91d4ecf16995362","tid":2474862,"uid":38805,"like":8,"dislike":7,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T05:51:59.000Z","msg":"垃圾post 咪推啦, 處劇透撚仲講到為大義而戰收皮啦, 剩係見到你地日日洗板就覺得好L 煩."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T06:52:32.000Z","msg":"為大義？唔通做惡作劇唔係大義，因為惡作劇被bam就係大義？<br />\n事情有分輕重，講嘢寫粒字再仆街都罪不至死<br />\n點解有啲人硬係要非黑即白，覺得有人犯錯判佢死刑就抵死<br />\n唔係話唔處理得，要處理就要公正公平<br />\n宜家唔係數人頭判死刑嗰種中世紀獵巫<br />\n如果做唔到依點，係都要用bam掣處理其他人言論<br />\n我都係建議唔搞好過搞<br />\n寫粒字玩下標題會少忽肉唔開心？<br />\n勇者塔貼圖po見到啲白姐姐孽瘤大波華有心理陰影添<br />\n洗唔洗一拳打爆個mon再衝上勇者塔po樓主屋企搵佢出嚟打一身先？<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXxBpiYcCFkqKUqKh8AGkaiWdemHUHzaqZZGjcTnryeN7?filename=FU1BYxx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFU1BYxx.gif&h=e1d5919a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8995cb8af068e18ea61fcfd88ff97765435183ad","tid":2474862,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T09:56:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78c1afc70bccee49cea95783dbd9936feda533c8","tid":2474862,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T10:58:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2453f8ca760697c9a629126afa4a7e1aef358992","tid":2474862,"uid":229502,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T11:12:48.000Z","msg":"雖然成日同樓主有衝突，幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5db0857a1e1252e472a589c9e7300597a1964db","tid":2474862,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2453f8ca760697c9a629126afa4a7e1aef358992","tid":2474862,"uid":229502,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T11:12:48.000Z","msg":"雖然成日同樓主有衝突，幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T11:32:14.000Z","msg":"對事不對人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b7da6f00698636331d24ff68c2ce4b2363d3b0","tid":2474862,"uid":73043,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T11:57:30.000Z","msg":"以前淨係睇海賊王動畫，未睇到就畀人劇透艾斯死咗...<br />\n真係唔會惡到叫人死全家咁撚反智囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反而仲引起我既興趣想繼續追落去。<br />\n當時俾人透左唔會覺得人地有問題。<br />\n反而係覺得自己問題，點解人地個個知，而我唔知<br />\n因為我唔睇漫畫，然後自己會走去睇埋漫畫。<br />\n<br />\n好撚老實既，自己睇動畫，睇到劇情想繼續追落去，要先睹為快，咪去睇漫畫囉。<br />\n<br />\n睇得動畫，就預撚左係其他渠道，有預先知道下集劇情嘅風險架啦。<br />\n<br />\n好似海賊王同火影（世界第一）咁，動畫劇情同漫畫差撚左成年。唔通又要為左動畫迷，隔成年先可以討論咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又好似鬼滅咁，早排紅果期都有動畫朋友知我睇完漫畫，會主動問我最後個呀妹點啦。我都會如實講俾佢聽。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好心真係咁鍾意套作品，就自己睇漫畫啦。<br />\n<br />\n自己懶去睇，睇一半唔睇一半，真係咁唔想知就唔好上社交媒體喇，明明係自己問題，唔小心睇到又咒人死全家，要全世界就你班懶人，點解呢個世界忽然咁撚反智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2a0ae0d58fcddd8f926062b9eebec71b8a42c5f","tid":2474862,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2453f8ca760697c9a629126afa4a7e1aef358992","tid":2474862,"uid":229502,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T11:12:48.000Z","msg":"雖然成日同樓主有衝突，幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T12:05:46.000Z","msg":"雖然成日同你有衝突，正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd901ded2b093038a7a5077cecab75f639cb334","tid":2474862,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T12:56:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bade2593c55ff13b35683a9d5e410b97188aebe8","tid":2474862,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T15:14:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18dc9c918953b02da830e7a18898ddb507d79646","tid":2474862,"uid":48132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T15:57:22.000Z","msg":"講得好"}]}